<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <!-- required meta tags -->
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">

        <!-- css -->
        <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">

        <!-- title -->
        <title>Hello friend!</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <h1>Hello From Afar</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <p>Dear @Model.GetRecipient(),</p>
                    <p>How are you? I hope that you are having a nice weekend. I'm vacationing in Iceland while I learn programming! </p>
                    <p>@Model.GetRecipient(), you would not believe how cold it is here. I should have gone to Hawaii instead.</p>
                    <p>But I like programming a lot, so I've got that going for me. </p>
                    <p>Looking forward to seeing you soon. I'll bring you back a souvenir. </p>
                    <p>Cheers,</p>
                    <p>Travel Enthusiast @Model.GetSender()</p>
                </div><!-- end .col-md-12 -->
            </div><!-- end .row -->
        </div><!-- end .container -->
    </body>
</html>
